OpenFlow.NBAPI
Class LinkLayerAddress

java.lang.Object
  OpenFlow.NBAPI.LinkLayerAddress

public class LinkLayerAddress
extends java.lang.Object

Retains (Ethernet MAC) link layer address in several forms.

On creation of a LinkLayerAddress, given a long or a byte array representation of the address, the other representation is computed and both are stored along with the string representation as immutable instance members of the class.
